headline: FedEx sends specialists to streamline European operations
summary: FedEx is targeting its European operation in the next round of cost cuts. Combining U.S. ground and Express networks requires careful balancing to maintain customer service. The post FedEx sends specialists to streamline European operations appeared first on FreightWaves.

headline: Do Wall Street Analysts Like FedEx Stock?
summary: FedEx has underperformed the broader market over the past year, but analysts are moderately optimistic about the stock’s prospects.
